'''2010年扬加列车脱轨事故'''是2010年6月21日发生在[[刚果共和国|刚果（布）]]境内的一起[[铁路事故列表|铁路事故]]。列车脱轨并冲入沟壑。最初的报道称至少60人死亡、数百人失踪，估计死亡人数可能继续上升。<ref name="60 killed in Congo train crash"/><ref name="Republic of Congo train crash kills scores"/>截至2010年6月23日，死亡人数已上升至76人，受伤人数达745人。<ref name="Congo train crash death toll rises to 76">{{cite news |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-congo-train-idUSTRE65M1LG20100623 |url-status=live |title=Congo train crash death toll rises to 76 |date=2010-06-23 |work=[[路透社|路透社]] |accessdate=2022-01-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220102093819/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-congo-train-idUSTRE65M1LG20100623 |archive-date=2022-01-02}}</ref>

1991年9月该国曾发生过类似事故，死亡100人，受伤300人，是该国历史上死亡人数最多的铁路事故。<ref name="Republic of Congo train crash kills scores"/> 根据《[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]]》统计的2002年以来铁路事故列表，本次铁路事故是2008年4月28日[[2008年胶济铁路列车相撞事故|中国胶济铁路列车相撞事故]]（至少70人死亡）以来最严重的一起。<ref name="The world's worst rail accidents">{{cite news |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/7847786/The-worlds-worst-rail-accidents.html |url-status=live |url-access=subscription |title=The world's worst rail accidents |date=2010-06-22 |work=[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]] |publisher=Telegraph Media Group |accessdate=2010-06-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109090619/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/7847786/The-worlds-worst-rail-accidents.html |archive-date=2020-11-09}}</ref>

==事故==
事发时出事列车正从[[黑角|黑角]]经由[[刚果大洋铁路|刚果大洋铁路]]开往[[布拉柴维尔|布拉柴维尔]]，<ref name="Republic of Congo train crash kills scores"/> 在距黑角约60公里、比林吉（Bilingi）和奇通迪（Tchitondi）之间的的扬加（Yanga）发生事故。<ref name="Around 50 killed in Congo train crash">{{cite web |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/amp/idUKTRE65L1ED20100622 |url-status=live |title=Around 50 killed in Congo train crash – report |publisher=[[路透社|路透社]] |accessdate=2022-01-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220102094628/https://www.reuters.com/article/amp/idUKTRE65L1ED20100622 |archive-date=2022-01-02}}</ref>有四节车厢脱轨，掉入沟壑中。<ref name="Sixty killed in Congo Republic train crash"/>当时报道至少51人死亡，另有12人受伤。<ref name=BBC10373571>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/africa/10373571.stm |title=Train crash in southern Congo 'kills 50' |publisher=BBC News Online |accessdate=2010-06-22 |archive-date=2019-02-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190214062527/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/africa/10373571.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

伤员和遗体被转移到相关地点。<ref name="Train crash in southern Congo 'kills dozens'">{{cite news |url=http://gbcghana.com/news/35115detail.html |url-status=dead|title=Train crash in southern Congo 'kills dozens' |date=2010-06-22 |work=加纳广播公司（Ghana Broadcasting Corporation) |accessdate=2010-06-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190331232720/http://gbcghana.com/news/35115detail.html |archive-date=2019-03-31 }}</ref>其中16人有生命危险。<ref name="Republic of Congo train crash kills scores">{{cite news |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/africaandindianocean/congo/7847776/Republic-of-Congo-train-crash-kills-scores.html |url-status=live |url-access=subscription |title=Republic of Congo train crash kills scores |date=2010-06-22 |work=[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]] |publisher=Telegraph Media Group |accessdate=2010-06-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190401042750/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/africaandindianocean/congo/7847776/Republic-of-Congo-train-crash-kills-scores.html |archive-date=2019-04-01}}</ref>关于伤者的照片中，有大量肢体受伤和轮椅使用者。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://english.people.com.cn/90001/90777/90855/7035809.html|title=50 killed in train derailment in Republic of Congo|date=2010-06-23|work=[[人民日报|人民日报]]|accessdate=2010-06-23|archive-date=2016-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160131084638/http://english.people.com.cn/90001/90777/90855/7035809.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>亲属聚集在黑角和多利西的火车站等待着亲人的最新消息。<ref name="60 killed in Congo train crash">{{cite news|url=http://www.rte.ie/news/2010/0622/congo.html|title=60 killed in Congo train crash|date=2010-06-22|work=爱尔兰广电新闻时事（RTÉ News and Current Affairs）|publisher=爱尔兰广电（Raidió Teilifís Éireann）|accessdate=2010-06-22|archive-date=2017-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170224053614/http://www.rte.ie/news/2010/0622/congo.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>据称财产受到“严重”损失。<ref name="Train crash in Congo kills at least 60 people over 300 injured">{{cite news|url=http://www.nationalturk.com/en/train-crash-in-congo-kills-at-least-60-people-over-300-injured-6030060|title=Train crash in Congo kills at least 60 people over 300 injured|date=2010-06-22|work=National Turk|accessdate=2010-06-22|archive-date=2018-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180319092838/http://www.nationalturk.com/en/train-crash-in-congo-kills-at-least-60-people-over-300-injured-6030060|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==原因==
事故原因尚未查明，<ref name="Train crash in southern Congo 'kills dozens'"/>但当局批评了超速行为。<ref name="Dozens Die As Train Plunges Into Ravine"/>事故发生时的列车处于弯道。<ref name="Sixty killed in Congo Republic train crash">{{cite news|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSTRE65L17Y20100622|title=Sixty killed in Congo Republic train crash|date=2010-06-22|work=[[路透社|路透社]]|accessdate=2010-06-22|archive-date=2010-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100626214030/http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSTRE65L17Y20100622|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==反应==
军队和红十字会人员进入始发区域援救相关人员。<ref name="Republic of Congo train crash kills scores"/>总统[[德尼·萨苏-恩格索|德尼·萨苏-恩格索]]在事发后召见了政府高层官员。<ref name="Train crash in southern Congo 'kills dozens'"/>

刚果共和国政府宣布全国哀悼三天。<ref name="Dozens Die As Train Plunges Into Ravine">{{cite news|author=Winter, Andy|url=http://news.sky.com/skynews/Home/World-News/Train-Crash-Kills-Dozens-In-Republic-Of-Congo-Speed-Blamed-For-Derailment-In-Central-Africa/Article/201006415653497?lpos=World_News_First_World_News_Article_Teaser_Region_4&lid=ARTICLE_15653497_Train_Crash_Kills_Dozens_In_Republic_Of_Congo%3A_Speed_Blamed_For_Derailment_In_Central_Africa|title=Dozens Die As Train Plunges Into Ravine|date=2010-06-23|work=Sky News|accessdate=2010-06-23|archive-date=2019-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190822053948/https://news.sky.com/?lpos=World_News_First_World_News_Article_Teaser_Region_4&lid=ARTICLE_15653497_Train_Crash_Kills_Dozens_In_Republic_Of_Congo:_Speed_Blamed_For_Derailment_In_Central_Africa|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

根据政府的正式声明，事故死者后事的相关费用由政府承担。哀悼日从事故发生次周的周六开始。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.dawn.com/wps/wcm/connect/dawn-content-library/dawn/news/world/19-republic-of-congo-train-crash-kills-at-least-48-hh-03|title=Republic of Congo train crash kills at least 48|date=2010-06-23|work=DAWN|publisher=Dawn Group of Newspapers|accessdate=2010-06-23|archive-date=2010-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100709034852/http://www.dawn.com/wps/wcm/connect/dawn-content-library/dawn/news/world/19-republic-of-congo-train-crash-kills-at-least-48-hh-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>

经过昼夜抢修，6月23日，铁路恢复通车。<ref>{{cite news |title=Le trafic relancé entre Pointe-Noire et Brazzaville |publisher=Les Dépêches de Brazzaville |page=1 |date=2010-06-25 |accessdate=2010-06-30 |language=fr}} </ref>

